MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Mirrors the AiD-Main pattern adapted for C#/.NET:

settings.json:
  - SessionStart hook → session_start.sh (context block + pre-flight)
  - Stop hook → session_stop.sh (closing checklist)
  - PostToolUse (Edit|Write) → lint_csharp.sh (dotnet format per-project)
  - Permissions: deny bin/, obj/, .dll, .pdb, .exe

hooks/:
  - session_start.sh: prints active plan phase, recent commits, pre-flight rules
  - session_stop.sh: closing checklist (build, test, CLAUDE.md, commit, push)
  - lint_csharp.sh: routes edited .cs file to owning project, runs dotnet format

commands/:
  - /build-check: dotnet build + dotnet test with report format
  - /phase-status: read PLAN.md + source files, report done/in-progress/next
  - /damage-audit: Phase 1 gate check — verify complex damage path is wired

