  copy-ctor/Clone(), serialize-one-collection + rebuild-indexes on
  [OnDeserialized], TryGet/sentinel defensiveness, components+*Atb as
  the ability framework, processor auto-discovery, async void caveats,
  ID-based cross-entity refs, save/load discipline, externalised tunables.
- docs/aurora/INDEX.md: source list, verification caveats, cross-source
  discrepancies (e.g. ground combat round cadence 3h vs 8h).
